{"tid":2354091,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"共產黨回應紐交所：彈出彈入好撚廢呀 其實你繼續打都得架 做咩縮呀廢閪","createTime":"2021-01-05T08:13:41.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-05T08:40:34.000Z","uid":21470,"like":13,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"96c841618e9cb3bf5c128d25f8e36ea6515cc5df","tid":2354091,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T08:13:41.000Z","msg":"北京：紐交所做法反映制度的任意性和不確定性<br />\n<br />\n紐約證券交易所公布，不再繼續對中移動、聯通及中電信實施除牌工作。<br />\n<br />\n在北京，外交部發言人華春瑩回應時表示，聯通和電信已作初步回應，近期美國一些政治勢力持續無端打壓在美上市的外國公司，反映規則和制度的隨意性、任意性和不確定性，希望美方尊重法治及市場，多做維護全球金融市場秩序和保護投資者合法權益，有益於全球經濟穩定發展的事情。<br />\n<br />\n華春瑩表示，打壓中國公司的行為對中國相關公司的直接影響是相當有限，但是將損害美國國家利益，以及美國資本市場的全球地位，重申美國的國際金融中心地位，有賴全球企業和投資者對美國規則制度包容性和確定性的信任。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1568747-20210105.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1568747-20210105.htm&d=QL2FFPepynYtbGyOTzoAG7Y5fiapVNQoBN5VkmpLYQk%3D&h=f23ec85f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1568747-20210105.htm&h=2aa87cf6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1568747-20210105.htm</a>"},{"pid":"6e4e9ba060e89be1105fdeab6b8f0c8635285d25","tid":2354091,"uid":152476,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T08:16:27.000Z","msg":"笑得好美國佬就係垃圾<br />\n學定普通話啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8b1983e242fb5c0ae685ab2b3cc8604fc765133","tid":2354091,"uid":387466,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T08:16:47.000Z","msg":"食住上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />dllm 真係呢"},{"pid":"913a09e0162ada4ce409c0525f854ae20d5f3d2d","tid":2354091,"uid":32667,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T08:19:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gi